title: Code Cleanup - Unused Variables
description: Fix TS6133 unused variable/parameter warnings by prefixing intentionally unused parameters with underscore convention.

tasks.description: Fix unused 'options' parameters - Find all TS6133 errors for 'options' parameter and rename to '_options' in expression/node and function files
Fix unused 'scope' and 'context' parameters - Rename unused 'scope' to '_scope' and 'context' to '_context' across affected files
Fix unused 'math' parameters - Rename unused 'math' dependency parameters to '_math' in factory functions where the dependency is declared but not used
Fix unused 'callback' and 'args' parameters - Rename to '_callback' and '_args' where these parameters are required by interface but not used in implementation
Fix remaining TS6133 errors - Address any other unused variable declarations not covered by previous tasks, apply consistent underscore convention

acceptanceCriteria: No functional changes to code behavior
